            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1701252724270-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1701252724270-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> into large pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>garlic</strong> (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Peel your <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and chop (or grate) finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1701252730279-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
