    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>hake karaage</strong> along side the <strong>brown rice</strong> and <strong>pak choi </strong>with<strong> </strong>the<strong> Japanese-style mayo</strong> as a dipping sauce on the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
